     I                                        1   3 WANLOT
     I                                        1   1 WNALPH
     I                                        2   30WNSEQ
     I* NEW LOT ID # (PLASTIC)
     I            DS
     I                                        1   3 WHNLOT
     I                                        1   20WHSEQ
     I                                        3   3 WHALPH
     I* INTERNAL PART NUMBER(FCETL11)
     I            DS
     I                                        1   5 A2BHB1
     I                                        6  10 A2BHB2
     I                                       11  12 A2BHB3
     I                                        1  12 W2PART
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  15 @KANBN
     I                                        1   1 @KK
     I                                        2   5 @ZETI
     I                                        8   8 @ID
     I                                        9  11 @PROC
     I                                        6   8 @THI
     I            DS
     I                                        1  45 PRC
